{
  "stem": "166.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "One day we come home from work, we cannot go to our barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We have another appel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They hang up three guys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were hanging them, just a ceremony of hanging them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The reason-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] during the alarm, they did some sabotage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were stealing a piece of rubber to put down on their wooden shoes on the bottom of the-- to put them on the soles because when they walk, the snow was glued onto the wooden.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were always higher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they steal a piece of rubber sole to put it down on the shoe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "For that, they hung them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Three guys they hung.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Then there were an incident that two guys run away again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We cannot go to our barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We didn't get our soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We had to stay and make exercise and push-ups.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then, after this two hours exercise and push-ups, everyone got 25 on their [INAUDIBLE] and then went to the barrack again.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Later on, we go to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And again every second day is an alarm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But the airplane still does not come and bomb.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Finally, the end of '43-- 1943-- all a sudden the airplanes start coming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There was an alarm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And right away, they are there-- the airmen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They start bombing so hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was raining with bombs that we did not know where to run.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "First of all, we were afraid to run to the high-rise building because we thought that they're going to see the high rise building out, because it's not smoked up with fog.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So they're going to bomb that so we're afraid to run.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So we were running in the forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they bombed everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It even rained in the forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
